<li><a href="http://www.hko.gov.hk/gts/time/conversion.htm" class="external text" title="http://www.hko.gov.hk/gts/time/conversion.htm" rel="nofollow">Gregorian-Lunar Calendar Conversion Table</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.absolutelyfengshui.com/baby-gender-calendar.php" class="external text" title="http://www.absolutelyfengshui.com/baby-gender-calendar.php" rel="nofollow">Chinese Baby Gender Calendar</a></li>
</ul>
</li>
<li><a href="http://chinesecalendar.orados.com/" class="external text" title="http://chinesecalendar.orados.com/" rel="nofollow">Chinese Lunar Calendar 2008 with 'Yellow Calendar'</a></li>
